From 9c5a33c1930eee51b723a97ea1d167167bb63de5 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: =?UTF-8?q?=C3=98yvind=20Harboe?= <oyvind.harboe@zylin.com>
Date: Mon, 30 Mar 2026 13:14:48 +0200
Subject: [PATCH 17/30] fix: add mock-cpu SDC dependency on util.tcl for Bazel
 sandbox
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

The SDC sources designs/src/mock-array/util.tcl which must be in the
sandbox. Use SDC_FILE_EXTRA to declare the dependency and source
$::env(SDC_FILE_EXTRA) for a portable Bazel-sandbox-compatible path.
Export *.tcl from the mock-array BUILD.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>
Signed-off-by: Øyvind Harboe <oyvind.harboe@zylin.com>
---
 flow/designs/src/mock-array/BUILD.bazel | 2 +-
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+), 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/flow/designs/src/mock-array/BUILD.bazel b/flow/designs/src/mock-array/BUILD.bazel
index 04b36977..1842c384 100644
--- a/flow/designs/src/mock-array/BUILD.bazel
+++ b/flow/designs/src/mock-array/BUILD.bazel
@@ -1,5 +1,5 @@
 exports_files(
-    glob(["*.v", "*.sv", "*.svh"], allow_empty = True),
+    glob(["*.v", "*.sv", "*.svh", "*.tcl"], allow_empty = True),
     visibility = ["//visibility:public"],
 )
 
-- 
2.51.0

